stories.title: Pakistan coast to facile win
stories.subTitle: Bangladesh v Pakistan, Asia Cup, 12th match
stories.summary: Pakistan capped their Asia Cup campaign with a comfortable win against Bangladesh, but that is small consolation for failing to reach the final, which India and Sri Lanka will contest on Sunday
